                    <h2>Full Job Description</h2>
                    <p>Are you a User Experience Designer with a track record of delivering intuitive digital experiences that drive results? Are you a strategic storyteller and systems thinker who can concept and craft smart, world-class campaigns across a variety of mediums?</p>
                </section>

                <section class="job-responsibilities">
                    <h2>The Work You'll Do:</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Support the Creative Directors and Associate Creative Directors of experience design to concept and oversee the production of bold, innovative, award-winning campaigns and digital experiences.</li>
